was able to access @elorea’s private sale the other week to pick up one of my fave fragrances from them, and had to photograph the packaging. I’m obsessed!

I’m a big fan of lighter, fresher fragrances (think Jasmine, Bergamot, Mandarin notes), so it’s no wonder I fell in love with this scent when I got the discovery set 🌊

a bit more of the notes:

top - bergamot, lemon, neroli, mandarin

middle - pocheon jasmin, ylang-ylang, white rose

base - cedar wood, white musk

so soothing yet energizing!
